%p Hello #{@resource.email}!

%p An account has been created for you with #{@resource.user_role} privileges.
%p Please change your password as soon as possible using the link below.

%p= link_to("Change my password", edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token))

%p If this email was not intended for you, please ignore this email.
%p Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.
